*{{Cite book|last1=Turner |first1=D.C.|last2= Bateson |first2=P. |title=The Domestic Cat: The Biology of its Behaviour|publisher=Cambridge University Press |year=2000|edition = 2 |isbn = 0521636485 |author=edited by Dennis C. Turner, Patrick Bateson.|ref=harv}}
