      <text xml:space="preserve">{{About|the mythical dog}}
{{Infobox mythical creature
|Creature_Name  = Cerberus
|Image_Name     = RomanCerberus.JPG
|Image_Caption  = Detail of [[sculpture]] of god [[Hades]] with Cerberus
|Grouping       = [[Legendary creature]]
